\par \lquote All\rquote s fair in love and war,\rquote  said Ron brightly, \lquote and this is a bit of both. Cheer up, it\rquote s the Christmas holidays, Luna\rquote ll be home!\rquote 
\par They had an excellent view of the village of Ottery St Catchpole from the breezy hillside to which they Disapparated next morning. From their high vantage point, the village looked like a collection of toy houses
