\par \lquote Well, it\rquote s not like you haven\rquote t just seen them. You were there for Christmas,\rquote  said Hermione coldly.
\par \lquote I wasn\rquote t at The Burrow!\rquote  said Ron, with an incredulous laugh. \lquote Do you think I was going to go back there and tell them all I\rquote d walked out on you? Yeah, Fred and George would\rquote ve been great about it. And Ginny, she
